                                        </Paragraph>
                                    </TableCell>
                                </TableRow>
                                <TableRow>
                                    <TableCell>
                                        <Paragraph Style="{StaticResource TableLabel}">
                                            结课考试
                                        </Paragraph>
                                    </TableCell>
                                    <TableCell>
                                        <Paragraph Style="{StaticResource TableText}">
                                            完成一到四课程阶段后，即可参加课程的结课考试
                                        </Paragraph>
                                    </TableCell>
                                </TableRow>
                                <TableRow>
                                    <TableCell>
                                        <Paragraph Style="{StaticResource TableLabel}">
                                            课程计划
                                        </Paragraph>
                                    </TableCell>
                                    <TableCell>
                                        <Paragraph Style="{StaticResource TableText}">
                                            通过结课考试之后，请于计划中获取您的课程任务，完成之后在此单元上传
                                        </Paragraph>
                                    </TableCell>
                                </TableRow>
                                <TableRow>
                                    <TableCell>
                                        <Paragraph Style="{StaticResource TableLabel}">
                                            设置
                                        </Paragraph>
                                    </TableCell>
